  | A | B |      MAPINT      |       MAPSETINT        |
  +---+---+------------------+------------------------+
  | 1 | 1 | map[1:1 2:1 3:1] | map[1:[1] 2:[2] 3:[3]] |
  +---+---+------------------+------------------------+
