  | [APPLIED] | A | B |      MAPINT      |        MAPSETINT         |
  +-----------+---+---+------------------+--------------------------+
  | true      | 1 | 1 | map[1:1 2:1 3:1] | map[1:[3 4] 2:[2] 3:[3]] |
  +-----------+---+---+------------------+--------------------------+
update lwt set mapint = mapint - {2} where a = 1 and b = 1 if exists;
